<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM4.7">
<l>vāṉāḷu māmatipōl veṇkuṭaikkīḻ maṉṉavartam</l>
<l>kōṉāki vīṟṟiruntu koṇṭāṭuñ celvaṟiyēṉ</l>
<l>tēṉārpūñ cōlait tiruvēṅ kaṭamalaimēl</l>
<l>kāṉāṟāyp pāyuṅ karuttuṭaiyē ṉāvēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I shall not esteem the wealth of [being] celebrated being seated majestically,</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming the king of kings, under the white [royal] parasol,</l>
<l rend="indent">like the great full moon that reigns over the sky.</l>
<l>I shall possess the design to flow as a jungle river</l>
<l rend="indent">upon the mountain of the sacred Veṅkaṭa,</l>
<l rend="indent">with gardens [full of] flowers brimming with honey.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
